UNOFFICIAL COPY 26 RS BR 2401
1 AN ACT relating to Medicaid.
2 Be it enacted by the General Assembly of the Commonwealth of Kentucky:
3 Section 1. KRS 205.5365 is amended to read as follows:
4 Notwithstanding any provision of law to the contrary and unless required under federal
5 law, the Department for Medicaid Services and any managed care organization with
6 which[whom] the department contracts for the delivery of Medicaid services are hereby
7 prohibited from expending any Medicaid funds on any of the following:
8 (1) Cross-sex hormones when prescribed or administered primarily or solely for the
9 treatment of gender dysphoria; and
10 (2) Gender reassignment surgery to alter or remove physical or anatomical
11 characteristics or features that are typical for and characteristic of a person's
12 biological sex.
